{
  "stem": "22910.1",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So I went there on-- on Pessach to my friend.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And I sat down to one of the tables.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "It was on Shabbat.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Well, before I got home, my father knew about it.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] Apparently, one of the boys went to his father, said, Lili was at that ice cream parlor in Tisou.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And they immediately went to my father saying, Lili was seen in the ice cream parlor.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So my-- and then, I'll never forget, because my father was so nice and gave so-- had so much faith in me, he said, if Lili was there, I'm sure she didn't do anything that was wrong.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he did not accept that.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And when I came home, he told me what was told and what he answered.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then he said, but it's a better idea for you not to go, because there's [YIDDISH] involved.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Which means that the way things look.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You have to be careful not to make other people stumble.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "In other words, they-- they gossiped unnecessarily.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And that in itself is some kind of transgression.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So I almost like caused it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So that part, he says, it's better idea not to do it.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But thinking back, I always think it was so nice of him to answer without knowing what really happened.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He had faith in me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And in general, my father was-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I was angry with my father a great deal because [LAUGHS] I felt he didn't do his job as a head of the family.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] [SIGHS] he was very nice to the children all the time.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And he never beat us or anything.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I got a spanking from my father just once in my life--",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
